## Why This Is Asked
This question assesses the ability to design runtime-extensible components, balancing modularity with operational safety in distributed, high-throughput systems.

## Key Concepts
- Strategy pattern: decouples limiter logic from engine
- Registry: dynamic, runtime-extendable mapping
- Factory: safe instance creation
