## Why This Is Asked

Tests the ability to design a runtime-extensible logging pipeline and to separate concerns via a plugin/registry pattern, while ensuring non-blocking behavior and per-channel configuration.

## Key Concepts

- Plugin/Registry pattern
- Non-blocking I/O and backpressure
- Interface design and TypeScript typing
